title: Late-Night Host Furious As Writer Puts Joke In His Monologue
description:
This behind-the-scenes look at The Late Night Comedy Hour shows off an intense interaction between the late-night host and his writer, who's in trouble for writing a joke instead of a political lecture. Sad. Not good!
